INSERT INTO `policies` (`id`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, '<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold text-slate-800\">1. 100% Client-Side Processing</h2>\r\n<p>Unlike traditional file compression or document modification platforms, ToolsGPT does not transmit, upload, or process your files on any external servers. All operations happen entirely within your browser\'s sandboxed local memory using client-side JavaScript, WebAssembly, and local browser canvas APIs.</p>\r\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900 rounded font-semibold inline-block\"><strong>🔒 Your original files never leave your device.</strong></div>\r\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold text-slate-800\">2. No File Storage or Ingestion</h2>\r\n<p>Because all processing is restricted to your machine, we have zero visibility or access to the documents, photographs, or proprietary contents you manage with our platform. We do not store, copy, monitor, parse, or share your data.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold text-slate-800\">3. Anonymous Analytics &amp; Metrics</h2>\r\n<p>We may gather minimal, aggregated analytics (such as feature click events, page loads, and device type statistics) to monitor service health, page loading performance, and support updates. None of this data is linked to personal identification details.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold text-slate-800\">4. Advertising Policy</h2>\r\n<p>We may partner with third-party networks to display relevant programmatic ads. These networks might utilize cookie IDs or generic browser characteristics to tailor advertising content. You can manage or disable behavior-based ad profiling in your browser privacy preferences.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold text-slate-800\">5. Contact Privacy Team</h2>\r\n<p>For questions concerning browser security, local sandboxing, or privacy policies, please write to us directly at:&nbsp;support@toolsgpt.net</p>', '2026-07-06 16:55:21', '2026-07-07 16:32:12');

