(2, 14, 'image-resize.blade', 'Compress Image', 'Optimize JPG, PNG, and WebP file sizes instantly with no quality loss.', 'compress-image', 'Professional Online Image Compressor', 'Optimize JPEG, PNG, and WebP images by up to 80% without visible loss in quality. Fully client-side processing keeps your photos 100% private.', '<p><strong>ToolGPT: Fast, Secure &amp; Free Image Compressor</strong></p>\r\n<p>Compress JPEG, PNG, and WebP images instantly without losing quality. OptiSqueeze is a powerful browser-based image compressor that reduces file sizes by up to 80% while keeping your images private. All processing happens directly on your device &mdash; no uploads, no accounts, and no waiting.</p>\r\n<p>Why Use OptiSqueeze?</p>\r\n<p>Large images slow down websites, affect SEO rankings, and consume extra bandwidth. OptiSqueeze helps you optimize images quickly with advanced compression tools while maintaining excellent visual quality.</p>\r\n<p>100% Private Client-Side Compression</p>\r\n<p>Your images never leave your device. OptiSqueeze processes everything directly in your browser, keeping your photos safe, secure, and completely private.</p>\r\n<p>Smart File Size Compression</p>\r\n<p>Need a specific file size? Set your target limit (50KB, 100KB, 500KB, or more), and OptiSqueeze automatically finds the best quality while staying within your required size.</p>\r\n<p>Bulk Image Compression</p>\r\n<p>Compress multiple images at once and save time. Upload your files, optimize them together, and download compressed images individually or as a ZIP file.</p>\r\n<p>Supported Formats</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\r\n<li>JPEG / JPG &mdash; Reduce photo size while preserving quality.</li>\r\n<li>PNG &mdash; Optimize images with transparency support.</li>\r\n<li>WebP &mdash; Convert and compress images for faster web performance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>How It Works</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Upload or drag your images into OptiSqueeze.</li>\r\n<li>Choose compression quality or target file size.</li>\r\n<li>Select your output format.</li>\r\n<li>Compress and download your optimized images instantly.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Fast, private, and completely free image compression directly in your browser.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is OptiSqueeze safe to use for sensitive photos?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, absolutely. OptiSqueeze is one of the most secure image compression utilities on the internet. It operates entirely client-side. This means your files are never uploaded to our servers, keeping your personal photos, contract screenshots, and sensitive graphics 100% private on your own hardware.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I compress an image to a specific KB size?\",\"answer\":\"To compress an image to a target size (for example, under 200 KB):\\r\\n\\r\\nClick on Compression Settings.\\r\\n\\r\\nSelect the Max File Size (KB) option.\\r\\n\\r\\nDrag the slider to your desired cap (e.g., 200 KB).\\r\\n\\r\\nRun your images through the queue. Our smart adaptive search loop will automatically adjust dimensions and quality to fit your target limit.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I convert my PNG images to WebP?\",\"answer\":\"Yes! OptiSqueeze acts as a format converter as well as a compressor. Under the Compression Settings pane, find the Export Format dropdown menu and select WebP. This will automatically transcode all optimized outputs to Google\'s highly efficient next-gen WebP standard.\"},{\"question\":\"Does OptiSqueeze support batch compression?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. You can drag and drop multiple images at once to load them into the batch process queue. The dashboard will show you exactly how many files are loaded, your aggregate file size before and after compression, and your total disk space savings.\"},{\"question\":\"Why does my compressed PNG file sometimes look the same size?\",\"answer\":\"Unlike JPEGs, PNG is a lossless format designed for graphics with transparency. Standard browser canvas compression algorithms can struggle to compress certain complex PNG files heavily without loss of quality. For maximum size reduction on photorealistic graphics, we highly recommend switching the output Export Format to WebP or JPEG.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a limit to the image file size I can upload?\",\"answer\":\"You can safely load individual image files of up to 50 MB. Because the processing uses your local browser\'s memory and CPU power rather than our server limits, performance depends on your device\'s speed.\"}]', '<svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\r\n                    <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path>\r\n                </svg>', '#ff6900', 'active', 'Fast, Secure & Free Client-Side Image Compressor', 'Compress JPEG, PNG, and WebP images by up to 80% instantly and securely. 100% client-side compression means your photos never leave your device. Complete bulk processing support.', 'image compressor, client-side image compressor, compress image under 50kb, bulk image optimizer, webp converter online, png compressor, secure photo shrinker, offline image compression, jpeg optimizer, optisqueeze', 118, NULL, 'image', '2026-07-07 13:21:17', '2026-07-14 14:15:55'),
(6, 14, 'image-crop.blade', 'Crop Images', 'Crop images locally. Zero uploads, 100% private.', 'crop-images', 'Crop Images Online Quickly & Easily', 'Secure, browser-based cropping tool. Your images never touch our servers — 100% processed locally on your device. Free forever, no registration needed.', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><em>(Place this content below your main cropper interface to provide context for users and readable text for search engine crawlers.)</em></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Secure, Fast, and Private Image Cropping with CropSafe</strong></h3>\r\n<p>In an era when digital privacy is paramount, editing sensitive or personal photos online shouldn\'t require you to compromise your data. <strong>ToolGPT </strong>is a revolutionary, free online image cropper designed entirely with user privacy and speed in mind.</p>\r\n<p>Unlike traditional online photo editors that force you to upload your files to external servers, CropSafe operates 100% client-side. This means the entire cropping and editing process happens locally, right inside your web browser. Your images never leave your device, ensuring complete security and zero risk of data exposure.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you need to quickly resize a profile picture, prepare an image for social media (using our handy 1:1, 16:9, or 9:16 aspect ratio presets), or fine-tune a photograph with precision zoom and rotation controls, CropSafe provides a seamless, professional-grade experience. It&rsquo;s lightning-fast because there are no upload or download wait times. Just drag, drop, crop, and save instantly in high-quality PNG, JPEG, or WEBP formats.</p>\r\n<p>Experience the peace of mind that comes with a truly private, no-upload image cropping tool.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is CropSafe really free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, CropSafe is completely free. There are no hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no account registration required.\"},{\"question\":\"Do you save or store my images?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely not. CropSafe is a client-side application. Your images are processed entirely within your own web browser and are never uploaded to our servers or stored anywhere else. Your privacy is 100% guaranteed.\"},{\"question\":\"What image formats can I edit?\",\"answer\":\"You can import most standard web formats, including JPEG, PNG, WEBP, and SVG.\"},{\"question\":\"What formats can I export my cropped image as?\",\"answer\":\"You can choose to download your final, cropped image as a high-quality PNG, a standard JPEG, or an optimized WEBP file. For JPEG and WEBP, you can even adjust the image quality to control the final file size.\"},{\"question\":\"Does CropSafe work on mobile devices?\",\"answer\":\"Yes! CropSafe is built with a responsive design, meaning it works flawlessly on desktops, tablets, and smartphones. You can easily crop images on the go directly from your mobile browser.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a file size limit for the images I can crop?\",\"answer\":\"Because processing happens on your device, the file size limit is generally determined by your device\'s memory and browser capabilities. However, it effortlessly handles standard high-resolution photos (e.g., up to 50MB) without issue, as there is no server upload bottleneck.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-frame\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 7l16 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 17l16 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M7 4l0 16\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 4l0 16\" />\r\n</svg>', '#10b981', 'active', 'Secure, Free Online Image Cropper', 'Crop images online instantly with toolsgpt. 100% private, secure, and free. No uploads required—all image cropping happens locally in your browser.', 'image cropper, photo cropper online, secure image editor, local image crop, browser image editing, free photo cropper, privacy-focused image tool, client-side cropper, Toolsgpt', 500, NULL, 'image', '2026-07-08 13:23:57', '2026-07-14 14:15:44'),
(7, 15, 'pdf-compressor.blade', 'PDF Compressor', 'PDF compressor, compress PDF online, reduce PDF file size.', 'pdf-compressor', 'Professional PDF Compressor', 'Optimize and reduce your PDF file size locally on your device. We prioritize your privacy — your documents never touch external servers or cloud storage.', '<p data-path-to-node=\"3\">Our Professional PDF Compressor is an enterprise-grade utility engineered for users who prioritize both data privacy and document efficiency. In an era where digital security is paramount, we have eliminated the need for server-side processing, ensuring your sensitive documents never leave your local environment. Whether you are handling confidential contracts, academic research, or high-resolution business reports, our tool provides a secure, streamlined way to manage your digital footprint without compromising file integrity.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong>Why Choose Our Client-Side Optimizer?</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Unlike traditional online conversion services that require you to upload your files to a cloud server&mdash;potentially exposing your data to third-party access or unauthorized storage&mdash;our application runs entirely within your browser. By leveraging advanced client-side processing, we utilize your computer\'s local hardware to analyze, re-encode, and optimize your PDF files in real-time. This \"offline-first\" architecture guarantees that your information remains in your possession from the moment you select the file until the optimized version is saved to your machine.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"6\">Precision Engineering for Every Use Case</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">We understand that document optimization is not a one-size-fits-all requirement. That is why our compressor features a sophisticated engine that balances compression ratios with visual fidelity.</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"8\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Recommended Mode:</strong> Our balanced preset, ideal for standard office documents and general distribution, providing significant size reduction while maintaining high readability.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Extreme Mode:</strong> Engineered for users facing strict upload limitations, this setting utilizes aggressive stream-level compression, making it perfect for documents containing high-density graphical elements or legacy data.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Low Compression Mode:</strong> Designed for high-stakes documents where maintaining every original bit of visual clarity is mandatory, focusing primarily on structural defragmentation and metadata cleanup.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong>Advanced Metadata Sanitization</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\">A frequently overlooked aspect of PDF security is the hidden data embedded within the file structure. Every PDF file often contains \"metadata\"&mdash;information regarding the software used to create the document, the author&rsquo;s name, creation dates, and sometimes even template history. Our tool includes an intelligent sanitization layer that automatically strips these unnecessary tags. This not only further reduces the final file size but also ensures that your professional documents are clean, safe, and free from sensitive tracking history.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong>Experience the Efficiency</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\">With an intuitive interface and a zero-configuration workflow, you can optimize your documents in seconds. Simply drag and drop, select your preferred settings, and download your optimized file. No sign-ups, no subscriptions, and no hidden costs&mdash;just pure, high-performance optimization built for the modern digital professional.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is my document data secure?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. This tool is built on a client-side architecture, meaning your PDF is never uploaded to a server or stored in the cloud. The processing happens entirely within your browser environment.\"},{\"question\":\"Are there any file size limits?\",\"answer\":\"Our browser-based engine is optimized for stability. You can comfortably compress PDF files up to 150 MB. For extremely large files, we recommend ensuring your browser tab remains active during the process.\"},{\"question\":\"Does compression reduce image quality?\",\"answer\":\"It depends on your selection. The \\\"Low Compression\\\" preset focuses on structural optimization, preserving full quality. The \\\"Extreme\\\" preset may downscale images to achieve maximum space savings.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool require an internet connection?\",\"answer\":\"While you need an internet connection to load the page initially, the actual compression engine functions offline. Once the page is loaded, your files are processed locally on your device.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this for password-protected files?\",\"answer\":\"This tool is designed to work with standard, unprotected PDF documents. If your file is encrypted with a password, you will need to remove the protection before uploading it to the tool.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-file-type-pdf\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M5 12v-7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M5 18h1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 -3h-1.5v6\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 18h2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M20 15h-3v6\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M11 15v6h1a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2h-1\" />\r\n</svg>', '#f43f5e', 'active', 'Professional Client-Side PDF Compressor | Secure, Fast & Private', 'Shrink your PDF files instantly in your browser. Our professional PDF compressor processes files locally, ensuring your data never leaves your device. Secure, free, and efficient.', 'pdf compressor, compress pdf, reduce pdf file size, pdf optimizer, shrink pdf, private pdf compression, secure pdf tool, browser based pdf compressor, client side pdf compression, free pdf resize, pdf file reducer, optimize pdf documents, fast pdf compression', 1, NULL, 'pdf', '2026-07-09 08:27:18', '2026-07-14 14:15:36'),
(8, 16, 'json-format.blade', 'JSON Formatter', 'Format, validate, and minify your JSON data in seconds.', 'json-formatter', 'JSON Formatter & Validator', 'Format, validate, parse, and minify your JSON data securely. Works entirely in your browser with no server-side processing.', '<h3 data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong>Efficient JSON Formatting and Validation</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) is the standard format for data exchange across modern web applications, APIs, and configuration files. While JSON is highly efficient for machines to parse, it is often delivered in a \"minified\" state&mdash;stripped of whitespace and indentation&mdash;making it extremely difficult for humans to read, audit, or debug. The JSON Formatter solves this by providing a clean, accessible interface to transform raw, compressed strings into structured, human-readable code.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong>How It Works</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">Using the tool is straightforward. Users simply paste their raw JSON into the input area or upload a JSON file. With a single click, the formatter parses the structure and displays it with consistent indentation, syntax highlighting, and logical nesting. If the JSON structure is invalid, the tool provides immediate feedback, highlighting potential syntax errors such as missing commas or unclosed brackets, which saves significant time during development.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong>Privacy and Security</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\">One of the primary concerns for developers when using online utilities is data security. This JSON Formatter operates entirely client-side. When you paste your data or upload a file, the processing happens locally within your browser. No data is sent to a server, stored, or indexed. This ensures that sensitive API responses, configuration data, or private logs remain strictly confidential and never leave your workstation.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong>Common Use Cases</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">API Debugging:</strong> Quickly format complex JSON responses from REST APIs to understand the data structure.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Configuration Management:</strong> Clean up configuration files to ensure they follow correct formatting standards before deployment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Data Analysis:</strong> Parse large, minified datasets exported from databases to make them readable for analysis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Code Documentation:</strong> Prepare clean JSON snippets for technical documentation or README files.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\">Whether you are a software engineer debugging a production issue, a student learning data structures, or a business analyst reviewing exported data, the JSON Formatter provides the clarity needed to work effectively. It is a reliable, high-performance utility designed to streamline your development workflow without compromising data security.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"What does this tool do?\",\"answer\":\"This tool takes raw, unformatted, or minified JSON data and transforms it into a readable, indented structure known as \\\"pretty-printing.\\\" It also performs syntax validation to identify errors, and it can minify JSON by removing all unnecessary whitespace for production use.\"},{\"question\":\"Is it free?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, this JSON Formatter is completely free to use. There are no registration walls, hidden subscriptions, or premium tiers. You can use all features\\u2014including formatting, minification, and file processing\\u2014as often as you need without any cost.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my data secure?\",\"answer\":\"Your data is highly secure. Because this tool functions entirely client-side within your browser, your information never leaves your computer. We do not transmit your data to any external server, meaning your sensitive API keys, configuration files, and private logs remain private.\"},{\"question\":\"Which file formats are supported?\",\"answer\":\"This tool is specifically designed for JSON (JavaScript Object Notation). It works natively with .json files. You can paste the text directly into the input area or upload your JSON files, and the tool will process them efficiently.\"},{\"question\":\"Does it reduce quality?\",\"answer\":\"No, formatting or minifying JSON does not change the data\'s logic, values, or structure. It only alters the presentation (spacing and indentation). The underlying data remains identical, ensuring your code remains functional and accurate after processing.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a file size limit?\",\"answer\":\"While the tool is optimized for performance, extremely large files\\u2014such as those measuring hundreds of megabytes\\u2014may cause browser performance issues due to memory constraints. For most standard development and configuration files, the tool handles data instantly.\"},{\"question\":\"Which browsers are supported?\",\"answer\":\"This tool is compatible with all modern web browsers, including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, and Opera. As long as you are using a current version of a major browser, the tool will perform optimally without needing extra plugins.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-json\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M20 16v-8l3 8v-8\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M15 8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4a2 2 0 1 1 -4 0v-4a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M1 8h3v6.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 -3 0v-.5\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M7 15a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 0 1 -1v-2a1 1 0 0 0 -1 -1h-1a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-2a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1\" />\r\n</svg>', '#8b5cf6', 'active', 'JSON Formatter: Format, Validate & Minify JSON Online', 'Instantly format, validate, and minify your JSON data with our free, secure, browser-based JSON Formatter. Ideal for developers needing clean, readable JSON code.', 'JSON formatter, JSON validator, JSON minifier, format JSON, pretty print JSON, JSON parser, online JSON tool, beautify JSON, JSON structure validator, clean JSON code.', 4, NULL, 'developer', '2026-07-09 09:33:10', '2026-07-14 14:15:28'),
(9, 20, 'age-calculator.blade', 'Age Calculator', 'Calculate your exact age in years, months, days, and more with our free, precision online Age Calculator tool.', 'age-calculator', 'Precision Age and Date Duration Calculator', 'Determine the exact duration between any two dates with high-precision calculations. Perfect for age verification, project tracking, and historical timeline analysis.', '<p data-path-to-node=\"25\">The Age Calculator is a precision-driven web utility designed to determine the exact duration between two specific dates. Whether you need to know how old you are, the age of a project, or the duration between two historical events, this tool provides an accurate breakdown in multiple time units.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">Users often rely on standard mental math for age, which can be inaccurate due to varying month lengths and leap years. This tool automates the process by performing complex date arithmetic, ensuring that you receive consistent results every time. Simply input your starting date and your target date to generate an immediate, comprehensive report.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\">Common use cases for this tool span both professional and personal domains. Developers and business owners use it to verify age requirements for services, HR departments use it for calculating tenure, and individuals use it for planning significant milestones or genealogy research. By providing results in years, months, weeks, days, hours, and minutes, the tool offers a granular view of time that is essential for legal compliance and precise scheduling.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">Beyond simple convenience, the Age Calculator is built with efficiency in mind. It processes all calculations locally within your browser, ensuring that your data remains private and secure. There is no server-side storage of the dates you input, making this a reliable and safe solution for checking age-related data.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\">The interface is optimized for speed and clarity. By presenting the output in a clean, organized dashboard, we eliminate the clutter often found on other calculation sites. Whether you are conducting a quick check or performing detailed time-based analysis, this calculator serves as a dependable utility for all your date-math needs.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"How accurate is the Age Calculator?\",\"answer\":\"Our calculator is highly accurate. It accounts for leap years and the specific number of days in each month. By calculating the exact number of milliseconds between two dates, it provides the most precise conversion possible into years, months, and days.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I calculate the age difference between two future dates?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. You can select any two dates, whether they are in the past, present, or future. The tool will calculate the exact duration between the two points, regardless of their chronological position.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool work on mobile phones?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. The interface is fully responsive, meaning it automatically adjusts to your screen size. Whether you are using a desktop computer, a tablet, or a smartphone, the functionality remains identical and easy to use.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my birth date data stored on your server?\",\"answer\":\"No. Your privacy is a priority. All calculations happen locally within your web browser. When you input dates, they are not transmitted to or stored on our servers, ensuring your data remains completely private.\"},{\"question\":\"Why does the result show months and days differently?\",\"answer\":\"Because months have different lengths (28, 29, 30, or 31 days), the calculation of \\\"months\\\" is relative to the specific calendar start date. Our tool uses standard calendar arithmetic to ensure consistency across the board.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this for business or legal purposes?\",\"answer\":\"While our calculator provides accurate mathematical results, it is intended for general informational purposes. For legal or critical financial documentation, please ensure you verify requirements with the relevant authorities.\"},{\"question\":\"What happens if I enter the wrong dates?\",\"answer\":\"The tool includes validation checks. If you enter an invalid date format, the calculator will prompt you to correct the input. You can use the reset button to clear the fields and start over at any time.\"},{\"question\":\"Are leap years factored into the calculation?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Our algorithms fully account for the Gregorian calendar, including leap years. This ensures that calculations spanning multiple years or decades remain mathematically correct and reliable.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-math-symbols\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 12l18 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M12 3l0 18\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M16.5 4.5l3 3\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M19.5 4.5l-3 3\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M6 4l0 4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 6l4 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M18 16l.01 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M18 20l.01 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 18l4 0\" />\r\n</svg>', '#000000', 'active', 'Precision Age Calculator Find Age in Years, Months, and Days', 'Calculate your exact age with our precise Age Calculator. Find your age in years, months, days, weeks, hours, minutes, and seconds. Free, accurate, and instant.', 'age calculator, how old am I, date of birth calculator, calculate age by date, age difference calculator, birthday calculator, age in days, age in months, time duration calculator, exact age finder, age from date of birth, chronologic age calculator, years months days calculator, personal age tool, precise age tool, how old am i in days, age counting tool, birth date math, time between two dates, age calculator online', 4, NULL, 'calculators', '2026-07-09 11:06:16', '2026-07-14 14:15:20'),
(10, 20, 'bmi-calculator.blade', 'BMI Calculator', 'A clinical-grade calculator for Body Mass Index analysis. Designed for accuracy and simple interpretation.', 'bmi-calculator', 'Professional BMI Calculator', 'Calculate your body mass index accurately and instantly. Get clear insights into your health status with our professional, easy-to-use tool.', '<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">Understanding your Body Mass Index (BMI) is a foundational step in monitoring your physical health. Our Professional BMI Calculator is designed to provide you with a quick, accurate, and easy-to-understand analysis of your weight relative to your height. Whether you are tracking fitness progress, consulting with a healthcare professional, or simply maintaining an awareness of your general well-being, this tool offers the reliability you need.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>What is BMI?</strong> BMI is a widely accepted screening tool used to categorize individuals into weight groups, such as underweight, healthy weight, overweight, or obese. It serves as an indicator of body fatness for most people. While it is not a direct measurement of body fat percentage or muscle mass, it provides a cost-effective and accessible way to assess potential health risks associated with weight.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong>How Our Tool Works:</strong> Our calculator utilizes the standard mathematical formula for BMI: weight in kilograms divided by height in meters squared. Because we understand that different regions and individuals prefer different measurement systems, we have built the tool to support both Metric (kg/cm) and US Imperial (lbs/ft/in) inputs. When you input your age, gender, height, and weight, our system calculates your BMI instantly. It then uses this number to classify your result according to established health guidelines.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Why Use Our Calculator?</strong> In today&rsquo;s fast-paced world, convenience is key. Our tool is built for the web, meaning you do not need to download software or install complex applications. You can access it directly from your browser. Furthermore, we prioritize your privacy. Unlike many other online tools that track user data, our calculator processes your input locally. Your personal health information is never sent to a server or stored in a database, ensuring that your privacy is maintained throughout the process.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong>Use Cases and Benefits</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Personal Health Monitoring:</strong> Keep a consistent log of your BMI to track changes over time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Fitness Planning:</strong> Use your BMI as a baseline metric when starting a new diet or exercise routine.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">General Awareness:</strong> Gain a quick snapshot of where your current weight falls within healthy ranges.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong>Important Considerations:</strong> While our calculator provides accurate results based on standard clinical formulas, it is important to remember that BMI is a screening tool. It does not account for variations in body composition, such as muscle mass vs. fat mass. Athletes and individuals with high muscle density may have a higher BMI that does not necessarily indicate health risks. We always recommend interpreting these results in consultation with a qualified healthcare professional who can consider your full medical history and lifestyle factors. Our calculator is designed to empower you with information, helping you make informed decisions about your health journey.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"What is the Body Mass Index (BMI)?\",\"answer\":\"BMI is a numerical value derived from your mass (weight) and height. It is defined as body mass divided by the square of body height, expressed in units of kg\\/m\\u00b2. It is primarily used as a screening tool to categorize individuals into weight categories to help identify potential weight-related health risks.\"},{\"question\":\"Is this BMI calculator accurate for everyone?\",\"answer\":\"While the formula is mathematically precise, BMI has limitations. It does not distinguish between muscle mass and fat mass. Therefore, highly muscular individuals, such as athletes, may have a high BMI score despite having a low body fat percentage. It is best used as a general indicator rather than a definitive medical diagnosis.\"},{\"question\":\"Why should I use this tool instead of others?\",\"answer\":\"Our tool prioritizes privacy and speed. We do not require account creation, nor do we track your inputs. Everything is processed directly in your browser. Additionally, our interface is clean, professional, and free from intrusive advertisements or distractions, allowing you to focus purely on your results.\"},{\"question\":\"How often should I check my BMI?\",\"answer\":\"Checking your BMI once a month or every few months is usually sufficient for most people. Fluctuations in weight can occur daily due to hydration, sodium intake, and other factors. Tracking trends over the long term is more valuable than focusing on minor, day-to-day changes in your number.\"},{\"question\":\"Does age and gender impact my BMI results?\",\"answer\":\"For the general population, the standard BMI formula is the same for men and women and does not change based on age. However, the interpretation of what constitutes a \\\"healthy\\\" BMI can sometimes vary for children and teenagers, where growth charts are used instead of the standard adult BMI ranges.\"},{\"question\":\"What are BMI Prime and Ponderal Index?\",\"answer\":\"These are additional metrics we include for a comprehensive view. BMI Prime is a modification of the BMI that compares your BMI to the upper limit of the healthy range. The Ponderal Index is another way to measure body shape that is often considered more stable across different heights compared to the standard BMI.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my personal health data safe?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, your data is completely safe. Because our tool operates entirely within your web browser, your measurements are never transmitted to our servers or stored on any external database. Once you close your browser tab, your information is gone, ensuring full confidentiality.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-math-integral-x\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2c2 0 2 -4 3 -9s1 -9 3 -9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 12l6 6\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 18l6 -6\" />\r\n</svg>', '#dd2d4a', 'active', 'Professional BMI Calculator | Accurate Body Mass Index Tool', 'Calculate your BMI instantly with our free, professional tool. Get accurate results for US and metric units. Simple, private, and easy to use. Try it now!', 'BMI calculator, body mass index, calculate BMI, free BMI calculator, health calculator, weight status, BMI formula, BMI index, healthy weight range, BMI for adults, metric BMI, imperial BMI, online weight calculator, body fat percentage, BMI prime, ponderal index, weight management, fitness calculator, professional BMI tool, check my BMI.', 13, NULL, 'calculators', '2026-07-09 12:55:36', '2026-07-14 14:15:12'),
(11, 19, 'password-generator.blade', 'Password Generator', 'Secure passwords are generated instantly in your browser.', 'password-generator', 'Professional Online Password Generator', 'Create cryptographically secure, high-entropy passwords directly in your browser. Protect your digital identity with customizable, instant, and reliable password generation.', '<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">In an era where digital threats are increasingly sophisticated, the strength of your credentials is the primary line of defense. The Professional Online Password Generator provides a high-performance, private, and efficient solution for creating cryptographically secure authentication strings. Whether you are a software developer setting up environment variables, an IT administrator managing infrastructure access, or an individual securing personal accounts, this tool delivers the complexity required to withstand modern brute-force attacks.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why Credential Strength Matters</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">Weak or predictable passwords remain the leading cause of account compromises. Most users rely on predictable patterns&mdash;such as birthdates, common dictionary words, or simple alphanumeric sequences&mdash;that automated tools can crack in seconds. Our generator eliminates this vulnerability by producing strings that prioritize high entropy, making them statistically unlikely to be guessed or reconstructed via dictionary attacks. By focusing on entropy, we ensure your credentials meet the rigorous standards expected in modern cybersecurity.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>How It Works</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">Security is not just about the output; it is about the process. Our tool utilizes browser-native cryptographic randomness, specifically designed to produce unpredictable sequences. When you adjust the character set or password length, or switch to passphrase mode, the logic runs entirely on your device. By avoiding server-side processing, we eliminate the risk of man-in-the-middle attacks or malicious server logging. Your generated data exists only on your machine until you copy it to your clipboard.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>Versatile Use Cases</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">The tool is built for a wide range of professional and personal scenarios:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Web Development:</strong> Generate high-complexity keys for API tokens, database connections, and encrypted configuration files.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Account Security:</strong> Create distinct, unique credentials for every service you use, preventing credential stuffing attacks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Administrative Access:</strong> Secure SSH keys, root passwords, and administrative dashboard access with ease.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Passphrases:</strong> Develop memorable yet secure passphrases for personal use, balancing human cognitive limits with machine-level security.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong>Privacy and Security Commitment</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">We believe that a security tool should be transparent. By keeping the entire generation process client-side, we provide a \"zero-trust\" experience. You do not need to worry about your passwords being stored on our servers because they never leave your browser environment. This approach provides the same security level as offline tools while retaining the speed and accessibility of a modern web application.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong>The Benefit of Entropy</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\">We include an integrated entropy meter to help you understand the strength of your password. Entropy, measured in bits, represents the log-base-2 of the total possible combinations for a password. A higher bit count indicates a higher level of security. By providing this measurement in real-time, we empower you to make informed decisions about the complexity of the passwords you use, ensuring you never settle for a \"weak\" or \"medium\" security level when protecting your most sensitive digital assets.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is my generated password stored anywhere?\",\"answer\":\"No. This tool operates entirely on the client side within your browser. We do not maintain databases, logs, or server-side memory to capture your passwords. Once you generate a string and copy it, it exists only on your local machine.\"},{\"question\":\"Why should I use a generated password instead of one I create?\",\"answer\":\"Human-created passwords are often predictable and prone to patterns based on personal experiences or easy-to-remember words. A generator removes human bias, creating high-entropy strings that are mathematically superior for resisting automated guessing attacks.\"},{\"question\":\"What is the difference between character mode and passphrase mode?\",\"answer\":\"Character mode generates random strings of symbols, numbers, and letters, which are harder to remember but highly secure. Passphrase mode uses a series of dictionary words, providing a longer string that is easier for humans to memorize while remaining incredibly difficult for machines to crack.\"},{\"question\":\"What does the \\\"Exclude Similar Characters\\\" option do?\",\"answer\":\"This feature removes characters that are easily confused, such as the uppercase \\\"I,\\\" lowercase \\\"l,\\\" the number \\\"1,\\\" and the digit \\\"0.\\\" This makes your password easier to read and manually type when copy-pasting is not an option.\"},{\"question\":\"What is entropy, and why is it displayed?\",\"answer\":\"Entropy is a measure of randomness. The higher the entropy (in bits), the more difficult a password is to brute-force. We display this value so you can instantly verify that your chosen password meets the security requirements of the platform you are securing.\"},{\"question\":\"Is this password generator suitable for enterprise environments?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is ideal for developers and system administrators who need to generate secure keys and credentials quickly without the overhead of enterprise-grade credential management software, provided you are following your organization\'s specific security protocols.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I save these passwords securely?\",\"answer\":\"We recommend using a dedicated, reputable password manager (such as Bitwarden or 1Password) to store your credentials. Our tool is designed to generate the secure string, which you should then transfer directly to your encrypted password vault.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-password-fingerprint\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 8c.788 1 1 2 1 3v1\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M9 11c0 -1.578 1.343 -3 3 -3s3 1.422 3 3v2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M12 11v2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M6 12v-1.397c-.006 -1.999 1.136 -3.849 2.993 -4.85a6.385 6.385 0 0 1 6.007 -.005\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M12 17v4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M10 20l4 -2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M10 18l4 2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M5 17v4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 20l4 -2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 18l4 2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M19 17v4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 20l4 -2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 18l4 2\" />\r\n</svg>', '#218380', 'active', 'Professional Online Password Generator | Secure & Private', 'Generate cryptographically secure, high-entropy passwords instantly. 100% client-side security. No data storage. Protect your accounts with PassGen today.', 'password generator, secure password maker, random password tool, strong password creator, online password generator, passphrase generator, high entropy password, password security tool, dev tools, web security, client side password, free password generator, password manager tool, generate secure passwords, random string generator, encryption key generator, privacy focused tool, browser based security, alphanumeric password, password strength checker', 1, NULL, 'security', '2026-07-09 13:25:14', '2026-07-14 14:15:02');
