(12, 18, 'word-counter.blade', 'Word Counter', 'Analyze your content in real-time. Count words, characters, and reading time instantly.', 'word-counter', 'Free Online Word Counter Tool', 'Instantly analyze your text with our accurate counting tool. Whether you are a student, blogger, or professional writer, get the insights you need to meet your length requirements effortlessly.', '<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">In the world of professional writing, academic research, and digital marketing, constraints are rarely suggestions&mdash;they are requirements. Whether you are crafting an essay with a strict maximum word count, writing a search-engine-optimized meta description, or drafting a social media post, hitting the right length is crucial. The Free Online Word Counter Tool is designed to provide the clarity and precision you need to master your content.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>What the Tool Does:</strong> This tool serves as an essential companion for anyone who works with text. By simply pasting your draft into the workspace, you receive an immediate breakdown of your content. It calculates the total number of words, characters, and sentences, while also estimating the average reading time. It eliminates the guesswork, allowing you to format your work to fit specific requirements perfectly.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong>How It Works: </strong>Simplicity is at the core of our approach. The tool operates using client-side processing, which means your text never leaves your browser. You type or paste your content, and the engine immediately parses the data. It recognizes common delimiters like spaces, punctuation, and line breaks to identify words and sentences accurately. Because the processing is local, the response time is near-instant, providing a smooth experience even for long-form documents.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Why It Is Useful:</strong> For students, the Word Counter ensures compliance with assignment rubrics, preventing penalties for going over or under designated limits. For content marketers and SEO specialists, it is a vital tool for optimizing headlines, meta descriptions, and body content to ensure they fit within the parameters required by search engines and social platforms. For creative writers, it offers insights into pacing by showing how sentence density changes throughout a narrative.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong>Privacy and Security:</strong> We prioritize your data security. Unlike many online tools that upload your work to a remote database, our Word Counter performs all calculations locally within your browser. Once you close the tab or clear the input, the text is gone from our interface. You can analyze drafts, private emails, or confidential documents with complete confidence, knowing that your content remains entirely under your control.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>The Benefits of Precision</strong> Writing is an iterative process. By having a reliable, fast, and accurate count of your work, you can edit with purpose. Instead of manually counting words or relying on word processors that might slow down your computer, our lightweight tool provides the data you need to produce concise, impactful, and compliant writing every time.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is this word counter tool completely free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is 100% free. There are no hidden fees, no subscriptions required, and no limits on how many times you can use the tool in a day. We believe that essential writing utilities should be accessible to everyone, from students to professionals, without barriers or costs.\"},{\"question\":\"How accurate is the word count?\",\"answer\":\"Our tool uses standard algorithms to identify words based on spaces and punctuation. It is highly accurate for standard English text and most professional documents. However, please note that unusual formatting, tables, or complex symbols may occasionally cause variations in counting compared to some proprietary word processors.\"},{\"question\":\"Do you save the text I input?\",\"answer\":\"No. Privacy is a foundational part of our design. All analysis occurs within your browser window. We do not store, log, or transmit your text to any server. Once you clear the input field or refresh the page, your content is removed from the tool\\u2019s memory.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I count words in multiple languages?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our word counter is designed to work with most languages that use standard spacing between words. While it is optimized for English, it will provide accurate word and character counts for any language that follows standard linguistic spacing rules.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a limit on how much text I can count?\",\"answer\":\"We do not impose a strict limit on the volume of text you can paste. However, for extremely large documents (like full-length novels or massive datasets), the browser\\u2019s performance might be impacted. For standard articles, essays, and reports, the tool will function smoothly and provide results instantly.\"},{\"question\":\"Why is my character count different in your tool versus Microsoft Word?\",\"answer\":\"Different programs interpret characters differently, particularly regarding spaces, line breaks, and special formatting characters. Our tool counts characters based on standard web-based definitions. If you need a specific type of character count (such as excluding spaces), we provide both total character counts to give you the most flexibility.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool provide grammar or spell checking?\",\"answer\":\"No, this tool is specifically optimized for word, character, and sentence counting. By focusing strictly on these metrics, we maintain a lightweight, fast, and privacy-focused experience. For grammar and spell checking, we recommend using dedicated proofreading software alongside our tool.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this on my mobile phone?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Our interface is built with responsive web design principles. Whether you are using an iPhone, Android device, or tablet, the Word Counter will automatically adjust to fit your screen size, allowing you to track your word counts while you are on the move.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-text-recognition\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 8v-2a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 16v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M16 20h2a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M12 16v-7\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M9 9h6\" />\r\n</svg>', '#62b6cb', 'active', 'Free Online Word Counter Tool | Accurate Text Analyzer', 'Need to meet a word count? Use our free online word counter tool. Instantly count words, characters, and reading time. Simple, fast, and secure.', 'word counter, free word counter, online word counter, character count, count words, word count tool, text analyzer, text statistics, word count for essay, count characters, word counter tool, reading time calculator, sentence counter, online text counter, fast word counter, word count checker, word counter online, character count online, word limit tool, word counter free', 15, NULL, 'text', '2026-07-09 14:06:59', '2026-07-14 14:14:39'),
(13, 14, 'jpg-to-png.blade', 'JPG to PNG', 'Convert JPEG images to high-quality PNG format instantly.', 'jpg-to-png', 'Professional Online JPG to PNG Converter', 'Convert your JPEG images to PNG files instantly in your browser. Fast, secure, and optimized for high-quality image processing.', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Streamline Your Workflow with Professional JPG to PNG Conversion</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">The need to switch between image formats is a daily requirement for web developers, digital marketers, and graphic designers. While JPEG is the industry standard for photography and general web usage, the PNG format remains essential for projects requiring transparency and lossless quality. Our professional-grade JPG to PNG converter provides a seamless way to handle these format transitions without compromising quality or security.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>Why Choose Our Browser-Based Converter?</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">In the current digital landscape, privacy and efficiency are paramount. Many online conversion tools rely on external server-side processing, which requires you to upload sensitive images to unknown cloud databases. Our tool takes a different, security-first approach. By leveraging modern browser technologies, all conversion logic is executed locally on your device. Your files never leave your computer, ensuring that your original images remain private and secure throughout the entire process.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>How It Works</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">Our tool is engineered for simplicity. When you select your JPEG files, the browser reads the image data directly from your local storage. It then processes this data to transform the encoding into the PNG format. Because this happens in your local environment, you do not need to worry about slow upload times or bandwidth restrictions. Once the conversion is complete, you can download your new PNG files instantly. It is a direct, efficient path from source to destination.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Essential Use Cases</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">This tool is optimized for a variety of professional and creative tasks:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Web Development:</strong> Converting JPEGs for better compatibility with design systems that require PNG assets.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Graphic Design:</strong> Preparing images to be converted into transparent graphics for use in marketing collateral.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Asset Management:</strong> Standardizing your image libraries to a single format to maintain consistency across project files.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Social Media Management:</strong> Quickly reformatting images to meet the specific requirements of different platforms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong>Key Benefits of PNG Over JPEG</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\">While JPEG is excellent for compact file sizes in photography, PNG is superior when your goals involve image quality and transparency. PNG files support alpha channels, meaning you can have transparent backgrounds&mdash;a feature entirely missing from standard JPEG files. Furthermore, PNG utilizes lossless compression, meaning the image quality does not degrade each time the file is saved or edited. By using our converter, you retain the highest possible quality for your graphic assets while gaining the flexibility that the PNG format offers.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong>Built for Performance and Reliability</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">We understand that you have work to get done. Our interface is stripped of unnecessary distractions and clutter, focusing entirely on the task at hand. With robust support for batch processing, you can convert dozens of images with just a few clicks. This tool is the perfect companion for anyone seeking a reliable, private, and high-performance solution for their daily image processing needs. By combining speed, quality, and a user-centric design, we provide a tool that fits perfectly into any professional or creative workflow.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Does this tool compress my images during conversion?\",\"answer\":\"Our tool focuses on format conversion. We strive to maintain the highest fidelity possible during the transition. While PNG files are generally larger due to their lossless nature, the tool ensures that no unnecessary quality is sacrificed, preserving the detail found in your original JPEG files.\"},{\"question\":\"Is it safe to convert sensitive images using this tool?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Our conversion process is 100% local. The images you select are processed within your web browser on your own hardware. No files are uploaded to a remote server, which means your sensitive data is never exposed to the public internet or external storage systems.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I convert multiple images at once?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Our tool supports batch processing, which allows you to drag and drop multiple JPEG files into the workspace at the same time. You can initiate a bulk conversion and download all the resulting PNG files quickly, saving you time and effort.\"},{\"question\":\"Will I lose transparency if I convert a JPEG?\",\"answer\":\"JPEG images do not support transparency natively. When you convert a JPEG to a PNG, the background will remain opaque. However, you will have a PNG file that supports transparency, which you can then edit further in graphic design software to remove backgrounds as needed.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool work on mobile devices?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, the tool is fully responsive and optimized for mobile browsers. You can perform conversions directly from your smartphone or tablet, provided your device has a modern web browser installed, making it convenient to work while on the move.\"},{\"question\":\"Are there any limits on file size or the number of images?\",\"answer\":\"We have optimized the tool to handle a wide range of file sizes and batch quantities efficiently. While extremely large file counts or massive high-resolution images depend on your browser\'s memory capacity, our tool is built to remain fast and responsive for typical professional workloads.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to install any software or plugins?\",\"answer\":\"No installation is required. This is a purely browser-based utility. Simply visit the page, upload your files, and start converting immediately. This eliminates the need for bulky software installations or periodic updates, keeping your system clean and fast.\"},{\"question\":\"What happens if I have an error during conversion?\",\"answer\":\"If an error occurs, the tool provides immediate, clear feedback. Since the processing is local, most errors are caused by unsupported file types or browser memory constraints. Ensure your files are standard JPEG\\/JPG format and refresh the page if you experience persistent issues.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-jpg\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M21 8h-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2v-4h-1\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M10 16v-8h2a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 8h4v6a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-1.5a.5 .5 0 0 1 -.5 -.5v-.5\" />\r\n</svg>', '#2563eb', 'active', 'Free JPG to PNG Converter | Secure Online Image Conversion', 'Convert JPG to PNG instantly in your browser. Batch process your images with high-fidelity, secure, and local processing. No uploads required. Try it now.', 'JPG to PNG, convert JPG to PNG, image converter, online image converter, PNG converter, batch image conversion, free image tool, JPG to PNG online, fast image converter, browser based converter, local image processing, secure image conversion, high quality PNG, JPEG to PNG, professional image tools, image format changer, convert images free, web based image tool, no upload converter, lossless PNG conversion', 3, NULL, 'image', '2026-07-10 14:21:30', '2026-07-14 14:14:28'),
(14, 14, 'png-to-jpg.blade', 'PNG to JPG', 'Transform PNG images to JPEG format instantly.', 'png-to-jpg', 'Free PNG to JPG Converter Online', 'Convert PNG files to high-quality JPG images effortlessly. Fast, secure, and free browser-based processing for all your image needs without file uploads.', '<h3 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Why Convert PNG to JPG?</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">PNG (Portable Network Graphics) and JPG (Joint Photographic Experts Group) serve different roles in digital imaging. PNG files are excellent for images requiring transparency or crisp, sharp lines like logos and icons. However, these benefits often come at the cost of larger file sizes. JPG files are the standard for web optimization, offering significant compression that results in smaller file sizes, which are ideal for web pages, email attachments, and document uploads where storage or bandwidth is a concern.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\">Our Free PNG to JPG Converter bridges this gap, allowing you to quickly transition from lossless PNG formats to optimized JPGs without compromising on visual quality.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong>How Our Browser-Based Converter Works</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\">Unlike traditional online tools that require you to upload your personal files to a remote server, our converter operates entirely within your browser using client-side technology. When you select a PNG file, the processing is performed locally on your own machine. This technical approach offers two major advantages: unparalleled privacy and exceptional speed. Because no data is transmitted over the internet to a third-party server, you can be confident that your private documents and photos remain safe on your device.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong>Key Benefits</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"25\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Speed and Efficiency:</strong> By avoiding server-side uploads and downloads, you bypass the latency associated with network traffic. The conversion happens as fast as your processor allows.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Zero Data Footprint:</strong> Since your files are never uploaded, there is no risk of them being stored on a server, harvested for data, or accidentally shared.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Unlimited Usage:</strong> We do not impose limits on how many times you can use the tool. Whether you are converting a single image for a blog post or hundreds of assets for a professional project, our tool is built to handle it.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Consistency:</strong> Our tool applies uniform compression settings across your entire batch, ensuring that the resulting library of images maintains a consistent look and file structure.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong>Common Use Cases</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\">This tool is invaluable for web developers needing to optimize images for page speed, students or professionals preparing documents for submission, and content creators looking to save storage space on their local machines. If you are preparing a large website for launch, converting your transparent PNG icons to opaque JPGs (where transparency is not needed) can drastically reduce your page loading times, improving both user experience and search engine optimization.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong>Privacy and Security</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\">In an era where data security is paramount, our commitment to browser-based processing sets us apart. You hold full ownership and control over your files from start to finish. Our tool provides a professional, reliable, and secure environment for your daily conversion needs, making it the preferred choice for privacy-conscious users.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is this PNG to JPG converter free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is completely free. We believe in providing accessible, high-quality professional tools for everyone. There are no hidden subscription fees, no paywalls for premium features, and no usage caps.\"},{\"question\":\"Will I lose image quality when converting to JPG?\",\"answer\":\"JPG is a lossy format, meaning some data is compressed to reduce file size. However, our tool includes quality control settings, allowing you to choose a high-quality setting (e.g., 90-95%) that minimizes visible degradation while still achieving efficient file sizes.\"},{\"question\":\"Is it safe to convert sensitive images?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Since our converter uses client-side technology, your images are never sent to a server. Everything happens locally on your computer, meaning your files are as safe as they would be using native photo editing software.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I convert multiple files at once?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is designed for batch processing. You can select and process dozens of files simultaneously, and our system will handle them sequentially before providing you with a simple download option for all finished files.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to install any software?\",\"answer\":\"No. This tool is web-based and runs entirely within your browser. There is nothing to download, install, or update. Visit the website, and the tool is ready to use immediately.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this on my mobile phone?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Our interface is fully responsive and optimized for mobile devices. You can convert images on your smartphone or tablet just as easily as you do on a desktop computer.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I choose the right quality setting?\",\"answer\":\"For web usage, a quality setting of 75-85% is usually sufficient to maintain good visuals while keeping file sizes small. For archival or print-ready files, we recommend using 90% or higher.\"},{\"question\":\"Will this tool work without an internet connection?\",\"answer\":\"Once the page is loaded in your browser, the conversion logic functions locally. However, you generally need an active internet connection to load the tool page initially, as it is a hosted web application.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-png\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M21 8h-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2v-4h-1\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 16v-8h2a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M10 16v-8l4 8v-8\" />\r\n</svg>', '#ffb703', 'active', 'Free PNG to JPG Converter Online | Batch Image Converter', 'Easily convert PNG files to JPG online. Fast, secure, browser-based tool for high-quality image conversion. No software installation required. Start today.', 'png to jpg, convert png to jpg, online image converter, free image converter, png to jpeg, batch image converter, fast png conversion, change png to jpg, image file converter, online png to jpg, browser image converter, jpeg converter, image format converter, png to jpg free, secure image conversion, high quality image converter, web image optimization, compress png to jpg, easy image conversion, image tool online', 3, NULL, 'image', '2026-07-10 14:45:19', '2026-07-14 14:14:20'),
(15, 14, 'qr-code-generator.blade', 'QR Code Generator', 'Create custom, high-performance QR codes in seconds.', 'qr-code-generator', 'Professional Online QR Code Generator', 'Effortlessly create, customize, and download high-resolution QR codes for any purpose. A professional solution for marketing, business, and personal digital connectivity.', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>What is the Online QR Code Generator?</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">The Online QR Code Generator is a professional-grade web tool designed to bridge the gap between physical media and digital content. In today\'s fast-paced environment, providing a seamless transition for your customers from print, signage, or displays to your digital presence is essential. Our tool simplifies this process by allowing users to generate, style, and export high-quality QR codes in a matter of seconds.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>How the Tool Works</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">Unlike many platforms that require you to sign up for accounts or navigate through complex menus, our generator is built for efficiency. You simply input your desired content&mdash;such as a website URL or text&mdash;select your preferred styling options, and the code updates in real-time. Because the generation happens locally within your browser, the performance is exceptionally fast, and the process is entirely private. Once you are satisfied with the look and feel, you can download your final asset as a high-quality image or vector file ready for immediate use.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why Users Need a Professional QR Code Tool</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">In modern marketing and business operations, a QR code is often the first point of contact between a consumer and a brand. A poorly generated or low-resolution code can lead to scanning failures, which reflects negatively on your professionalism. Our tool provides customization options&mdash;such as logo integration and color matching&mdash;that allow you to present a polished, branded image. Whether you are creating menus for a restaurant, business cards for networking, or call-to-action signs for retail, high-quality QR codes are a necessity.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Key Benefits of Our Browser-Based Approach</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">Our tool is designed with a \"privacy-first\" mindset. Since all processing occurs within your browser, no data is sent to our servers for the actual code generation. This makes it an ideal solution for businesses handling proprietary links or sensitive contact data. Furthermore, being a browser-based application, it works on any device with an internet connection, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones, ensuring you can create codes whenever and wherever you need them.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>Versatile Use Cases</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">The potential applications for our QR Code Generator are vast. Businesses use our tool for:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Marketing Campaigns:</strong> Directing customers from print ads to promotional landing pages.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Networking:</strong> Creating codes that automatically add contact information to a smartphone.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Retail/E-commerce:</strong> Connecting physical product tags to online stores or detailed product specifications.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Event Management:</strong> Simplifying guest check-ins or providing access to event schedules.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,4,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Personal Use:</strong> Sharing Wi-Fi credentials, digital portfolios, or social media profiles easily.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">By choosing our professional QR Code Generator, you are investing in a tool that prioritizes performance, visual clarity, and user privacy. We have removed the friction typically associated with generating digital assets, allowing you to focus on your business goals rather than technical hurdles. Start creating custom, professional-grade QR codes today and take your digital engagement to the next level.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is this QR code generator completely free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is free to use for both personal and commercial purposes. You can generate, customize, and download as many QR codes as you need without any hidden fees or account requirements.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use the QR codes I generate commercially?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. All QR codes created with our tool are yours to use. You are free to include them on your commercial packaging, marketing materials, advertisements, and business documentation without restriction.\"},{\"question\":\"Do the QR codes I generate ever expire?\",\"answer\":\"No, the QR codes you generate do not expire. As long as the URL or data you encoded remains active and accessible, the QR code will continue to function correctly indefinitely.\"},{\"question\":\"What file formats can I download?\",\"answer\":\"We support industry-standard formats including PNG and SVG. PNG is ideal for web use and general documents, while SVG provides a vector format that is perfect for professional printing at any size without losing quality.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my data stored on your servers?\",\"answer\":\"Your privacy is a priority. All QR code generation is performed locally within your browser. We do not store, track, or save the information you input, ensuring your data remains secure and private.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I add my own logo to the QR code?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our generator includes a feature that allows you to upload and embed your own logo. This is a great way to personalize your code and make it instantly recognizable as part of your brand.\"},{\"question\":\"Will the QR code still work if I change the colors?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, however, it is important to maintain high contrast between the foreground (the code itself) and the background. As long as your selected colors provide sufficient contrast, the QR code will remain perfectly scannable.\"},{\"question\":\"How can I ensure my QR code is scannable?\",\"answer\":\"We recommend using high-contrast colors and avoiding overly complex or cluttered designs. Additionally, ensure the code is printed at a size that is large enough for mobile cameras to focus on clearly.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-qrcode\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1l0 -4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M7 17l0 .01\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1l0 -4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M7 7l0 .01\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M4 15a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1l0 -4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 7l0 .01\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 14l3 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M20 14l0 .01\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 14l0 3\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 20l3 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 17l3 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M20 17l0 3\" />\r\n</svg>', '#215e61', 'active', 'Professional Online QR Code Generator | Free & Custom', 'Create custom QR codes online for free. Add your logo, adjust colors, and download high-resolution QR images for print or digital use. No account needed.', 'QR code generator, create QR code, free QR code maker, custom QR code, QR code with logo, print QR codes, marketing QR code, URL to QR, business QR code, QR image generator, high resolution QR code, QR code maker online, professional QR codes, scannable QR, custom colors QR, digital QR code, generate QR code, QR code for website, contact QR code, QR code tool', 2, NULL, 'image', '2026-07-10 16:03:30', '2026-07-14 14:14:10'),
(16, 15, 'pdf-merge.blade', 'PDF Merger', 'Combine multiple PDF files into one secure document instantly.', 'pdf-merge', 'Free Online PDF Merger and Document Combiner', 'Seamlessly combine multiple PDF documents into a single file directly in your browser. Rearrange files easily with secure, client-side processing that ensures your private data never leaves your device.', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Simplify Your Document Management</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">Managing digital paperwork often involves dealing with scattered, fragmented files. The Free Online PDF Merger is a professional, browser-based utility designed to solve this exact problem. It allows users to combine multiple PDF documents into a single, organized file effortlessly. Whether you are compiling corporate reports, merging monthly invoices, or assembling a creative portfolio, this tool streamlines your document management process without requiring expensive software subscriptions or complex tutorials.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>How the PDF Combiner Works</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">Using the tool is incredibly straightforward and designed for immediate productivity. You begin by selecting or dragging your desired PDF files into the secure digital workspace. Once added to the browser interface, you can visually rearrange the order of the files to ensure your final document flows in a logical sequence. After arranging the order, a single click initiates the merging process. Within seconds, your new, consolidated PDF is generated and ready for download. There are no confusing settings to configure&mdash;just a clean, efficient, and reliable workflow.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why You Need a Dedicated PDF Merger</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">Dealing with dozens of separate email attachments is frustrating for both the sender and the recipient. By merging related documents into one cohesive file, you present a highly professional image and make information significantly easier to read, print, and share. This tool eliminates the friction of document compilation, saving you valuable time and reducing digital clutter on your hard drive. It transforms disorganized files into a unified presentation.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Common Professional Use Cases</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">Professionals across various industries rely on PDF merging software daily. Legal teams use it to combine case files, contracts, and evidence into single comprehensive dossiers. Real estate agents merge property details, disclosures, and financial statements for their clients. Students and educators combine research papers, lecture slides, and assignment guidelines into single study guides. Additionally, job seekers and freelancers often merge their cover letters, resumes, and portfolio pieces into one unified application document to impress potential employers.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>Uncompromising Privacy and Security</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">Traditional online PDF tools often require you to upload your sensitive documents to remote servers for processing, creating significant privacy risks. Our PDF Merger utilizes advanced modern web technologies to process your files entirely client-side. This means the merging logic happens directly inside your device\'s local memory. Your personal data, financial records, and confidential business documents never leave your computer, ensuring complete data security and compliance with strict data privacy standards.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong>The Browser-Based Advantage</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Because the tool operates entirely within your web browser, it offers unparalleled accessibility and convenience. There is no need to install bulky desktop applications, deal with licensing keys, or worry about recurring software updates. It works instantly on Windows, Mac, and Linux machines, provided you have a modern web browser installed. This lightweight, web-first approach ensures lightning-fast performance without draining your system resources or compromising your device\'s security.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is it safe to merge confidential documents using this tool?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, it is completely safe. Unlike many online tools, our PDF merger processes your files locally within your web browser. Your documents are never uploaded, stored, or transmitted to external servers, guaranteeing total privacy for your sensitive data.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a limit to how many PDF files I can merge at once?\",\"answer\":\"You can merge multiple files simultaneously. While there is no strict numerical limit imposed by the tool, the performance ultimately depends on your device\'s available memory and the combined file size of the PDFs you are processing.\"},{\"question\":\"Will merging my PDFs reduce their visual quality?\",\"answer\":\"No, the merging process does not degrade the quality of your documents. The tool seamlessly stitches the files together while preserving the original resolution, text clarity, layout formatting, and embedded elements of the source PDFs.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I rearrange the order of my files before merging?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Once you have added your files to the workspace, you can easily drag and drop them into your preferred sequence using the intuitive interface. The final merged document will reflect the exact top-to-bottom order you created.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to install any software to use this tool?\",\"answer\":\"No software installation is required. This is a fully web-based application that runs directly in your browser. Simply open the webpage, add your files, and start merging immediately without downloading any third-party programs.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool work on Mac and Linux computers?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our PDF merger is completely platform-independent. Because it runs securely in the web browser, it works flawlessly across all major operating systems, including macOS, Windows, Linux, and modern mobile operating systems.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I merge password-protected PDF files?\",\"answer\":\"Currently, the tool requires standard, unlocked PDF files to perform the merge successfully. If your documents are encrypted or password-protected, you will need to remove the security restrictions before adding them to the merger.\"},{\"question\":\"How much does it cost to use the PDF merger?\",\"answer\":\"The tool is completely free to use. There are no hidden fees, no required subscriptions, and no premium tiers. You get full access to all merging features without needing to create an account or provide payment information.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-file-text\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M17 21h-10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-14a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M9 9l1 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M9 13l6 0\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M9 17l6 0\" />\r\n</svg>', '#ef4444', 'active', 'Merge PDF Files Online Free | Secure Document Combiner', 'Securely combine multiple PDF files into one document directly in your browser. Free, fast, and private PDF merger with no file uploads required.', 'pdf merge, merge pdf files, combine pdf online, free pdf merger, pdf combiner tool, join pdf files, merge pdf documents, secure pdf merge, browser based pdf tool, merge pdf without upload, offline pdf merger, combine multiple pdfs, pdf page organizer, merge pdf offline, free document merger, stitch pdf together, arrange pdf pages, merge invoices pdf, combine reports pdf, pdf file binder', 3, NULL,