(17, 15, 'pdf-split.blade', 'PDF Split', 'Extract individual pages from any PDF document instantly.', 'pdf-split', 'Professional Online PDF Splitter', 'Easily extract specific pages from your PDF documents with our secure, browser-based splitter. Manage your digital paperwork with precision and efficiency.', '<h3 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Efficient Document Handling</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">Managing large digital documents often requires isolating specific content for reports, presentations, or record-keeping. Our PDF Split tool provides a professional-grade solution for extracting pages from any PDF document without the need for complex, expensive software. Designed for reliability and speed, this browser-based utility empowers users to take control of their document workflow instantly.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>How It Works</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">The process is engineered for simplicity and efficiency. By leveraging modern browser technology, the tool processes your files locally on your machine. When you upload a document, our engine reads the internal structure of the PDF, allowing you to select and isolate specific pages or extract the entire document into individual segments. Because the heavy lifting happens within your own browser environment, the tool operates at the speed of your hardware, providing a snappy, responsive experience regardless of file size.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why You Need It</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">Professionals frequently encounter oversized documents that need to be broken down. Perhaps you need to extract a specific contract page from a lengthy agreement, isolate an invoice from a financial report, or share a single chapter from a research paper. Our PDF Split tool removes the friction from these tasks. By providing a clean interface and robust functionality, it helps you eliminate redundant pages and focus on the content that matters most.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Privacy and Security Advantages</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">In an era where data security is paramount, our tool stands out by avoiding the risks associated with cloud-based document processing. Because we do not upload your files to an external server, your sensitive information remains on your local drive. This makes our tool an ideal choice for legal, medical, and corporate environments where data privacy protocols are strict. You get all the convenience of an online tool without compromising the security of your private data.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>Browser-Based Advantages</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">The primary benefit of a browser-based tool is accessibility. Whether you are working on a Windows PC, a Mac, or a mobile device, our PDF Split tool is ready when you are. There is no software to download, no installation to manage, and no updates to track. Simply visit the website, upload your file, and process your document on the fly. This platform-agnostic approach ensures you can maintain your productivity wherever your work takes you.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong>Key Benefits</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"30\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Zero Cost:</strong> Professional splitting capabilities available for free.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Speed:</strong> Instant extraction thanks to local processing.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Privacy:</strong> Files are processed locally, ensuring high-level data protection.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ease of Use:</strong> Drag-and-drop interface for a seamless user journey.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,4,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Reliability:</strong> Consistent output that preserves document quality every time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">By choosing our PDF Split utility, you are choosing a more organized, efficient, and secure way to manage your PDF files. Experience the difference that a dedicated, user-centric document tool can make in your daily professional or personal routine.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is it free to use this PDF Split tool?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is completely free to use. We provide professional-grade document splitting capabilities without any subscription fees or hidden costs. You can process as many documents as you need at any time.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to upload my files to a server?\",\"answer\":\"No. Our tool processes your PDF files locally within your web browser. Your documents are never uploaded to an external server, which ensures that your sensitive information remains private and secure on your own device.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I extract all pages at once?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Our tool features a batch processing option that allows you to extract every page of your PDF into individual files automatically. It is the most efficient way to break down large documents quickly.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool work on mobile devices?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is fully responsive and optimized for use on smartphones and tablets. As long as you have a modern web browser and a PDF file on your device, you can use our splitting service anywhere.\"},{\"question\":\"Is the quality of my PDF preserved?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. We use high-quality extraction methods to ensure that your documents remain identical to the original. Text, images, and formatting are preserved perfectly during the splitting process, maintaining the integrity of your work.\"},{\"question\":\"What should I do if my PDF is password protected?\",\"answer\":\"Currently, this tool is designed for standard, open PDF documents. If your file is encrypted with a password, you will need to remove the protection using a standard PDF reader or security software before our tool can process it.\"},{\"question\":\"Is there a limit to the file size?\",\"answer\":\"Our tool is built to handle standard documents efficiently. While it is optimized for most common PDF sizes, extremely large files with high-resolution imagery may require more browser memory. We recommend standard file sizes for the best performance.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to install any software?\",\"answer\":\"No installation is required. This is a fully web-based application. You do not need to download, install, or update any software. Simply open the tool in your browser and start splitting your PDF files immediately.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-dual-screen\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M5 4l8 3v15l-8 -3l0 -15\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M13 19h6v-15h-14\" />\r\n</svg>', '#723ec3', 'active', 'Professional Online PDF Splitter | Extract Pages Instantly', 'Easily extract specific pages from your documents with our secure, browser-based PDF Split tool. Fast, free, and private. Start splitting your PDFs today.', 'PDF Split, PDF splitter, split PDF, extract PDF pages, PDF page separator, free PDF splitter, online PDF tool, document management, PDF page extractor, break PDF pages, separate PDF, secure PDF split, browser-based PDF tool, split large PDF, PDF file manager, PDF organization, PDF processing, extract pages from PDF, fast PDF splitter, professional PDF utility', 2, NULL, 'pdf', '2026-07-11 04:19:34', '2026-07-14 14:13:51');
INSERT INTO `tools` (`id`, `category_id`, `view`, `name`, `taq_line`, `slug`, `title`, `short_title`, `content`, `faq`, `icon`, `color`, `status`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `meta_keyword`, `usages`, `badge`, `cat_slug`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(18, 18, 'character-counter.blade', 'Character Count', 'Precision text analysis for professionals and writers.', 'character-count', 'Free Online Character Counter Tool', 'A precise online character counter that provides instant, real-time statistics for your content, including word, sentence, and paragraph counts.', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Precision Text Analysis for Modern Professionals</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">In the digital age, content creators, researchers, and developers operate within strict constraints. Whether you are crafting a social media post, submitting an academic abstract, or optimizing metadata for SEO, knowing the exact character count of your text is essential. Our Free Online Character Counter Tool provides a high-performance solution for monitoring your text length, structure, and readability metrics in real-time.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>How It Works</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">Our tool utilizes a lightweight, browser-based engine to analyze your text as you interact with it. By leveraging client-side scripts, the application evaluates the character string length, word frequency, and grammatical structures such as sentences and paragraphs. Because the processing occurs locally within your browser, the tool operates at high speed, removing the need for server requests and ensuring an immediate feedback loop.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why You Need a Dedicated Counter</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">Standard word processors often provide basic counts, but they can be cumbersome and bloated. Our dedicated counter focuses exclusively on the data that matters most to writers: character counts with and without spaces, word counts, sentence density, and reading duration. By isolating these metrics, you gain a clearer understanding of your content&rsquo;s structure, which is crucial for meeting publication standards, platform-specific character limits, or project constraints.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Common Use Cases</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">The versatility of this tool makes it indispensable for various professionals. SEO specialists use our counter to check title tags and meta descriptions against search engine display limits. Academic writers utilize the tool to verify that their abstracts or footnotes remain within mandatory submission bounds. Additionally, social media managers rely on our tool to ensure their copy fits perfectly within platform constraints, while copywriters use it to verify the brevity and impact of their headlines.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong>Privacy and Browser-Based Advantages</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">One of the primary benefits of using a professional browser-based tool is the emphasis on data security. Unlike cloud-based platforms that might store or track your inputs, our tool performs all analysis locally. Your content remains on your computer. This makes it a secure choice for professionals handling sensitive drafts, legal documents, or proprietary business communications. Furthermore, being web-native means you do not need to download or update bulky software; it is always accessible via any modern browser, ensuring maximum productivity regardless of your operating system.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong>A Streamlined Editing Workflow</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Editing is an iterative process. Our tool supports this by offering built-in formatting options, such as case conversion, which allows you to standardize your text instantly. By combining analysis with basic formatting, we provide a centralized utility that reduces the need to toggle between multiple applications. This streamlined approach keeps your focus on the quality of your writing, not on the tools used to measure it.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"Is this character counter tool completely free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our character counter is entirely free. We believe that essential writing utilities should be accessible to everyone, from students and bloggers to professional editors and content strategists. There are no subscriptions, hidden fees, or premium tiers required to access the full functionality of the tool.\"},{\"question\":\"How is the estimated reading time calculated?\",\"answer\":\"Our reading time feature is based on an average reading speed of 200 words per minute. This is an industry-standard benchmark used to provide a realistic estimate of how long it takes an average adult to read your content, helping you tailor your writing to your audience\'s attention span.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my text data secure when using this tool?\",\"answer\":\"Privacy is a fundamental aspect of our design. All text analysis is performed locally within your web browser. This means your text is never sent to a server, processed in the cloud, or stored on any external database. Your work stays on your device.\"},{\"question\":\"Does this tool count characters with spaces included?\",\"answer\":\"Our tool provides two separate character metrics: one that includes spaces and one that excludes them. This dual reporting allows you to satisfy different requirements, whether you are following a strict character limit that includes spaces or looking to understand the pure density of the text content.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this tool on a mobile device?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. The tool is built with a responsive, mobile-first design philosophy. Whether you are using a smartphone, tablet, or desktop computer, the interface adapts seamlessly to your screen size, providing the same high-performance functionality and clean user experience across all devices.\"},{\"question\":\"What is the difference between word count and character count?\",\"answer\":\"A character count tracks every single symbol in your text, including letters, numbers, punctuation marks, and spaces. A word count specifically tracks groupings of characters separated by spaces. Both metrics are important: word count helps determine document length, while character count is vital for strict technical limitations like social media inputs or SEO fields.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this for bulk text or very long documents?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our tool is optimized for performance and can handle a high volume of text. While browsers have memory limits, you can comfortably process thousands of words at once. For exceptionally long manuscripts, we recommend breaking the text into chapters to maintain the best browser performance and readability.\"},{\"question\":\"Do I need to create an account to save my settings?\",\"answer\":\"No account creation is necessary. We designed this tool for speed and efficiency, so you can start working the moment the page loads. Your settings and text input are managed in your current session, and you are not required to log in or provide personal details to analyze your documents.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-abc\">\r\n	<path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 16v-6a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v6\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M3 13h4\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M10 8v6a2 2 0 1 0 4 0v-1a2 2 0 1 0 -4 0v1\" />\r\n	<path d=\"M20.732 12a2 2 0 0 0 -3.732 1v1a2 2 0 0 0 3.726 1.01\" />\r\n</svg>', '#ff0052', 'active', 'Free Online Character Counter Tool | Real-Time Text Stats', 'Get precise character, word, and sentence counts instantly. Our free online character counter tool is built for writers, editors, and content professionals.', 'character counter, word counter, text statistics, online character count, count characters, word count tool, character count app, text analysis tool, writing utility, content editor, character counter free, precise text stats, length checker, sentence counter, paragraph counter, reading time calculator, text processor, character counter online, word frequency, character limit checker', 2, NULL, 'text', '2026-07-11 04:55:14', '2026-07-14 14:13:43'),
(19, 16, 'base64-encoder.blade', 'Base64 Encoder', 'Effortlessly convert text and files to Base64 format.', 'base64-encoder', 'Professional Base64 Encoder and Decoder', 'A fast, secure, and reliable browser-based tool to encode text and files into Base64 format and decode them back to their original state instantly.', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Understanding Base64 Encoding</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">Base64 encoding is a fundamental process in computer science that transforms binary data into an ASCII string format. This conversion allows data to be safely transmitted over media that only supports text. By representing binary information as a sequence of printable characters, Base64 ensures that your data remains intact during transfer through systems that might otherwise misinterpret non-textual bytes.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong>How Our Base64 Encoder Works</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">Our tool simplifies this technical process into a user-friendly experience. When you provide input, such as a plain text string or an uploaded file, the application executes a standardized algorithm to calculate the Base64 representation. The tool handles character encoding standards, such as UTF-8, ensuring that special characters are encoded correctly without data loss. The decoding function performs the inverse, accurately reconstructing the original content from the Base64 sequence.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong>Why Developers Need This Tool</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">In modern web development, Base64 is ubiquitous. Developers frequently use it to embed small images directly into CSS files to reduce HTTP requests, or to encode binary data into JSON strings for API communications. Manually executing these conversions can be error-prone and time-consuming. Our tool acts as a dedicated utility, providing an immediate, reliable solution that fits seamlessly into your daily development cycle.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong>Common Use Cases</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\">The utility of a Base64 encoder extends across various technical domains:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Web Asset Optimization:</strong> Embedding icons and small images directly in stylesheets.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Data Transport:</strong> Converting binary files for inclusion in XML or JSON data structures.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Email Systems:</strong> Handling non-text attachments in MIME-encoded email protocols.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Authentication:</strong> Encoding credentials for Basic Auth headers in HTTP requests.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,4,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Debugging:</strong> Converting encoded strings to verify contents during API integration testing.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong>Privacy and Local Execution</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\">One of the most significant advantages of our browser-based approach is the commitment to data security. Unlike many online tools that send your data to a remote server for processing, our application performs all encoding and decoding operations locally on your machine. This means your sensitive, proprietary, or private data never leaves your environment, providing peace of mind during your development process.</p>\r\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong>Performance and Reliability</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">Our tool is built for high-performance execution. It is optimized to handle substantial input sizes without hanging the browser or introducing lag. The clean, professional interface is free of intrusive advertisements or unnecessary bloat, ensuring that you can perform your tasks with maximum speed. Whether you are a full-stack developer, a system administrator, or a security professional, this tool provides the consistency and reliability required for professional-grade work.</p>', '[{\"question\":\"What is Base64 encoding?\",\"answer\":\"Base64 encoding is a way to represent binary data as a sequence of ASCII characters. It is commonly used to transfer data over media that are designed to handle text, ensuring the data remains intact and readable after transport.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my data safe when using this tool?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Our tool performs all operations locally in your browser. Your data is never uploaded to a server, processed by a backend, or stored in a database, ensuring complete privacy and security.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use this for large files?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, the tool is designed to handle various file sizes. However, extremely large files may impact browser performance. It is recommended for use with standard assets like icons, small images, or text documents.\"},{\"question\":\"Why should I encode images to Base64?\",\"answer\":\"Encoding small images to Base64 allows you to embed them directly into HTML or CSS. This technique helps reduce the number of HTTP requests required to load a webpage, potentially improving initial render times.\"},{\"question\":\"What character encoding is supported?\",\"answer\":\"The tool primarily uses UTF-8 encoding, which is the standard for modern web development. This ensures that most international characters and symbols are handled accurately during the encoding and decoding process.\"},{\"question\":\"Is this tool free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, our Base64 encoder is completely free for all users. We believe in providing essential developer utilities without barriers to entry or hidden fees.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I copy the result?\",\"answer\":\"We have included a convenient \\\"Copy\\\" button near the output area. Simply click it, and the converted Base64 string or decoded text will be copied to your system clipboard for immediate use.\"}]', '<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\r\n  <desc>\r\n    Microprocessor Computer Chip 64 Bit Streamline Icon: https://streamlinehq.com\r\n  </desc>\r\n  <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M23.5762 16.5818c-0.6489 -0.1903 -1.3185 -0.3008 -1.9942 -0.3291l-0.8176 0.1297c0.1197 -1.2963 0.1795 -2.6822 0.1895 -3.9884 0.1388 0.06 0.2875 0.0938 0.4387 0.0997 0.7272 0.2484 1.5163 0.2484 2.2435 0 0.0458 0 0.0912 -0.0091 0.1335 -0.0266 0.0424 -0.0175 0.0808 -0.0432 0.1132 -0.0756 0.0324 -0.0325 0.0581 -0.0709 0.0757 -0.1133 0.0175 -0.0423 0.0265 -0.0877 0.0265 -0.1335 0 -0.0458 -0.009 -0.0912 -0.0265 -0.1336 -0.0176 -0.0423 -0.0433 -0.0808 -0.0757 -0.1132 -0.0324 -0.0324 -0.0708 -0.0581 -0.1132 -0.0756 -0.0423 -0.0176 -0.0877 -0.0266 -0.1335 -0.0266 -1.1666 -0.2293 -1.1068 -0.5285 -2.6822 -0.1595 0 -1.3461 0 -2.68224 -0.0998 -3.86879 0.1239 0.03492 0.2508 0.05828 0.3789 0.0698 0.3494 0.11981 0.7179 0.1739 1.0869 0.15953 0.389 -0.02374 0.7757 -0.07707 1.1566 -0.15953 0.0837 -0.0141 0.1597 -0.05738 0.2145 -0.12219 0.0548 -0.0648 0.0849 -0.14692 0.0849 -0.23178 0 -0.08487 -0.0301 -0.16699 -0.0849 -0.23179s-0.1308 -0.10809 -0.2145 -0.12218c-1.1167 -0.15954 -1.1367 -0.49855 -2.6921 -0.15954 -0.2493 -3.38017 -0.4288 -3.89866 -3.5796 -3.9884 0.0351 -0.12721 0.0585 -0.25738 0.0698 -0.38887 0.229 -0.73029 0.229 -1.51318 0 -2.243475 0 -0.045829 -0.0091 -0.09121 -0.0266 -0.133551 -0.0175 -0.042341 -0.0433 -0.080812 -0.0757 -0.113219 -0.0324 -0.0324059 -0.0708 -0.0581119 -0.1132 -0.0756501C17.0168 0.00902677 16.9714 0 16.9256 0c-0.0459 0 -0.0912 0.00902677 -0.1336 0.0265649 -0.0423 0.0175382 -0.0808 0.0432442 -0.1132 0.